data.description: The search is over! This impeccably renovated home  surpasses new construction in both quality and value. 5676 Baffin Rd. has just undergone a full renovation, bringing contemporary elegance and modern convenience to every corner. Step inside to discover a newly updated interior boasting modern finishes, including a remodeled kitchen and sleek appliance package, fresh flooring and paint throughout the entire home, eye-catching fixtures, and so much more. You'll also discover appealing landscaping and a new deck perfect for outdoor gatherings or a quiet retreat.     One of the unique features of this property is its financing opportunityCoan assumable VA loan option with a incredibly low-interest rate, making it easier than ever to own your dream home.    The main level welcomes you with an open-concept layout, featuring a bonus room with endless possibilities, a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace, a formal dining area, and a gourmet kitchen. Upstairs, a spacious loft offers versatility such as a home office, playroom, entertainment area, or additional living space. The luxurious master suite includes a walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Three additional bedrooms share a beautifully updated bathroom, ensuring ample space for everyone. The daylight basement is a spacious blank canvas, waiting to be finished according to your preference. Your proximity to major highways, shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options ensures convenience at your fingertips.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a fully renovated home with unique financing and potential for customization in the beautiful Fairburn, GA. Schedule your showing today and envision the possibilities at 5676 Baffin Rd!
